sequenceDiagram
    participant CP as Charge Point (Tool)
    participant CS as Central System (SUT)

    Note over CP,CS: Reusable State: Booted
    Note over CP,CS: Table 199, Section 3.22, Page 173

    CP->>CS: BootNotification.req
    Note right of CP: chargePointVendor = <Configured Vendor Name><br/>chargePointModel = <Configured Model>

    CS-->>CP: BootNotification.conf
    Note over CS: Validation: status should be Accepted

    loop Send per connector and connectorId=0
        CP->>CS: StatusNotification.req
        Note right of CP: status = Available
        CS-->>CP: StatusNotification.conf
    end

    Note over CP,CS: State is Booted
